commit.message:
[aarch64/arm] Updating the cost table for xgene1.

2018-11-23  Christoph Muellner <christoph.muellner@theobroma-system.com>

	* config/arm/aarch-cost-tables.h (xgene1_extra_costs): Update the cost table
	for Xgene1.

From-SVN: r266411
